        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2061",
        "content": "The French did not.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2061_147110_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2061/147110/2061_147110_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2061",
        "content": "The burning of Canso and the attack on Annapolis stirred up the wrath of New England.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2061_147110_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2061/147110/2061_147110_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2061",
        "content": "A wild enthusiast, William Vaughan, urged Governor Shirley of Massachusetts to make an immediate counter-attack.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2061_147110_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2061/147110/2061_147110_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2061",
        "content": "Nor could they be blamed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2061_147110_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2061/147110/2061_147110_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2061",
        "content": "Shirley was dejected and in doubt what to do next.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2061_147110_000006_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2061/147110/2061_147110_000006_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2061",
        "content": "All the merchants were eager for attack.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2061_147110_000009_000003",
